node.text:
The 2020 Blade Stealth 13 offers new features, components, and a few design tweaks. Its upgraded Nvidia GeForce GTX 1650 Ti graphics chip makes it the only true 13-inch gaming laptop available, and a new 120Hz display is even more appealing for gamers. These improvements on an already solid design make it easy to recommend, even if it’s less of a total overhaul than the Editors’ Choice-winning 2019 version was.

node.text: No, the iPhone 13 won’t be bringing back the headphone jack. Apple has lined up other big changes for this phone, though. Check the link in our bio for a full rundown on the latest iPhone 13 rumors.
